description: Retrieves the current settings of the AWS IoT Events logging options.

nested_items.name: loggingOptions
nested_items.description: The current settings of the AWS IoT Events logging options.

nested_items.name: roleArn
nested_items.description: The ARN of the role that grants permission to AWS IoT Events to perform logging.

nested_items.name: enabled
nested_items.description: If TRUE, logging is enabled for AWS IoT Events.

nested_items.name: detectorDebugOptions
nested_items.description: Information that identifies those detector models and their detectors (instances) for which the logging level is given.

nested_items.name: detectorModelName
nested_items.description: The name of the detector model.

nested_items.name: keyValue
nested_items.description: The value of the input attribute key used to create the detector (the instance of the detector model).
